NAME
     9x more scum & rats than rio. Just say NEIN.

SYNOPSIS
     9x [-v]

DESCRIPTION
     9x is a scummy X11 window manager. A rat infested rio rip-off.
     It provides far more than you bargained for.
     Do 9 things and do them poorly.

OPTIONS
     -v  Erase computer. Weep.

MOUSE
   Desktop & Bar
     Button 1  Window menu.

     Button 2  Desktop menu.

     Button 3  Sweep new terminal.

     Scroll    Cycle desktops.

   Window Menu
     Button 1  Focus.

     Button 2  Delete.

     Button 3  Sweep.

   Window Borders
     Button 1  Resize.

     Button 2  Delete.

     Button 3  Move.

     B1 + B3   Maximize.

KEYBOARD
     Alt+Space         Broom cupboard.

     Alt+Tab           Cycle windows.

     Alt+Shift+Tab     Reverse cycle windows.

     Alt+F4            Delete.

     Alt+F10           Maximize.

     Alt+F11           Fullscreen.

     Alt+[1..9]        Desktop 1-9.

     Alt+Shift+[1..9]  Window to desktop 1-9.

LAUNCHER
     Return     Sweep.

     Tab        Complete.

     Backspace  Delete.

     Down       Next.

     Up         Previous.

     Escape     Cancel.

CUSTOMIZATION
     Read the goddamn src(1) you filthy heathen.

BUGS
	 Your windows are dirty. You must sweep them first.

     Programs that depend on EWMH/ICCCM may shit the bed.

     Cursed cursors & Caerbannog bunnies lurking in dark corners...
